<div class="cards">
	<div class="form-block">
		<h4>VIP卡激活确认 </h4>

		<p>请再次核对以下信息是否正确</p>

		<%=form_for :card, :url=>activate_card_path do |f|%>
			<%=f.hidden_field :no,:value=>@card.no%>
			<div class="field">
				<label class="field-label field-label-long">待激活VIP卡号 : </label>
				<span class="field-plain"><%=@card.no%></span>
			</div>

			<div class="field">
				<label class="field-label field-label-long">充值预存款帐号 : </label>
				<span class="field-plain"><%=@card.member_card.user.login_name if @card.member_card && @card.member_card.user%></span>
			</div>

			<div class="field">
				<label class="field-label field-label-long">充值金额 : </label>
				<span class="field-plain">&yen;<%=@card.value%></span>
			</div>

			<div class="field">
				<label class="field-label field-label-long">VIP卡持有人手机号码 : </label>
				<span class="field-plain"><%=@card.member_card.buyer_tel if @card.member_card%></span>
			</div>

			<div class="field">
				<%=f.submit "确认激活",:class=>"btn submit"%>
				<%=link_to "取消",vip_path,:class=>"btn cancel"%>
			</div>

		<%end%>

	</div>
	<div class="tips-block">
		<p>小贴士</p>
		<ul>
			<li>
				<strong>如何激活我的VIP卡?</strong>
				<div>答：</div>
			</li>
			<li>
				<strong>怎么用VIP卡里面的余额付款?</strong>
				<div>答：</div>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div class="clear"></div>
	<div class="other-tip "> <span class="required">*</span> 小贴士 :  如果在激活过程中有什么疑问，请致电寻求帮助。客服电话：021 - 22306630 。</div>
	
</div>